{"word":"G3851 - παραβουλεύομαι - parabouleúomai - par-ab-ool-yoo'-om-ahee - Not regard","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραβουλεύομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parabouleúomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ab-ool-yoo'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Not regard</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எண்ணாதிரு"},{"paragraph":"to consult amiss"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and the middle of <a href=\"#/G1011 - βουλεύω - bouleúō - bool-yoo'-o/1011\">G1011</a>; to <i>misconsult</i>, that is, <i>disregard:</i> - not (to) regard (-ing).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}